    Doc fixes:
    * RT#86007 - Restore meaning for divorced sentence

6.67_04 Mon Jun 10 20:18:25 BST 2013
    Bug fixes
    * Address RT#85406, where specifying 'meta-spec' in
      META_[ADD|MERGE] would remove all prereqs (bingos)

